cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE. 

The paper introduces a framework for building interactive NLP and IR systems, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Software Engineering (cs.SE). However, given the focus on NLP and IR systems, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely categories.
